articles.title: Shaw Plaza losing its spark? Closures of Mui Kee and Picolino raise bigger questions
articles.summary:

📊 주요 수치: ,, ,, ,
📝 싱가포르 최신 동향
articles.content: There’s a silent churn happening at Shaw Plaza, Balestier’s once bustling neighbourhood mall. What’s more telling is that both restaurants are part of the prestigious Les Amis Group. Surprisingly, it wasn’t announced through the brand’s official socials. Likewise, Picolino, an Italian bistro tucked just a few units away, quietly shut its doors earlier this month without much hoo-ha. Both restaurants were launched with much anticipation during Shaw Plaza’s post-renovation revival in 2023, but it seems that initial excitement has waned. articles.title: S'poreans aged 21 to 59 can now claim $600 SG60 vouchers
articles.summary:
📰 제목: 21 59 $600
📊 주요 수치: 21, 59, 2025
📅 날짜: July 22
📝 July 22부터 시행
articles.content: Singaporeans aged 21 to 59 in 2025 can start claiming their $600 SG60 vouchers from July 22. Ms Low said that more than $127.6 million has been spent to date. Some $76.6 million has been spent at hawkers and heartland merchants, and more than $51 million at supermarkets. The list of participating outlets is available on go.gov.sg/sg60voucher.

articles.summary:
📰 제목: 싱가포르 최신 뉴스
🔍 주요 키워드: 그랩(GRAB)
📊 주요 수치: ,, ,, ,
📝 그랩(GRAB)이(가) , 기록
articles.content: Take a jaunt down Koon Seng Road where you’ll find the popular eye-candies adorned in ceramic Peranakan floral motifs, geometrical tiles, pastel hues and even Chinese couplets which are said to bring good fortune. While you can’t photograph its interiors, Rumah Bebe has eye-catching cerulean exteriors and bright Peranakan tiles that your ‘gram desperately needs. Lace up and grab your camera – we’re going shophousing.
